About me

I'm a Full Stack Developer and a Digital Marketing enthusiast. I'm on a mission to discover as much as possible about web. From design to development, analytics, data, machine learning, I want to know it all.

With a background in marketing, I gained valuable skills such as data analysis, SEO, UI/UX, branding, growth hacking, social media and many more from working in different projects.
